{"tid":1690348,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［全新抗爭模式］所有日程表唔可以有特定時間同地點","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:38:24.000Z","uid":41458,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4df3672b0a6c98adcabdd70c3985cfef67291fdd","tid":1690348,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無需再black bloc</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<strong>原本black bloc目的</strong><br />\n「不被認出」，難以被target<br />\n<strong>黑警應對black bloc方法</strong><br />\n「鳩拉」，black bloc 會成為佢地主要目標，預告集會等於邀請黑警拉你，佢地預先派大量便衣，green objects 埋伏，係人都拉，只衫就拉，black bloc 失去意義<br />\n<strong>不再black bloc理由</strong><br />\nblack bloc已失去功用，改以街坊look混入人群，如果黑警要鳩拉，必令全市民極度反感，到時淺藍會大幅轉軚<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不再預告時間地點，只預告日期同行動</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<strong>原本預告時間點目的</strong><br />\n「聚人」，大型遊行吸引國際目光<br />\n<strong>黑警應對遊行集會方法</strong><br />\n全方位目無法紀咁打壓，放tg, 執路， 鳩拉，以阻止人群聚集<br />\n<strong>不再預告時間地點</strong><br />\n黑警無法預先安排便衣，無法埋伏，無法封路<br />\n全新抗爭形式，只預告日期同行動，不預告時間地點。因為我地嘅手足遍全港，隨時開花冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">快閃行動，敵我難分，吸引國際目光</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>原因</strong><br />\n由於黑警增援部署需時，快閃變得極為安全，而冇事先預告，令安全行動時間增加，建議15mins為最長行動時間，之後各自和平散去<br />\n活動類型，記得拍片blur樣<br />\n<strong>黑警難以拉人</strong><br />\n快閃，黑警未到已經散咗，由於不再black bloc, 令黑警難以辨認邊個有參與<br />\n<strong>活動提議</strong><br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全民lunch快閃唱國歌</strong></span>，願榮光歸香港，一個帶頭，其他人自然會跟，最緊要拍片，後製要遮樣<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民搭車唱香港國歌</span></strong><br />\n- 歡迎大家諗其他創意活動，記住，係要以<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">吸引國際注意，搶佔頭版</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武請自行小組行動，無需理會網上號召，以智力敵，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n本人不支持一切犯法行為，新抗爭方法主要畀和理非，對抗黑警全面police state<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對，請講下你意見"},{"pid":"49b4240445a4fca72269c40f73ebb882fccd3eec","tid":1690348,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301b1534e697f3326cd3956a67f353c3c82ecf73","tid":1690348,"uid":127494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"eb4590c4d73a07e0e3404157950ac9bbfdbec3a6","tid":1690348,"uid":243446,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"Black bloc係一定要 唔係嘅話真係唔知邊啲係手足"},{"pid":"a456bc7751ae56cc43f5df5acd53381a32361ab4","tid":1690348,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb4590c4d73a07e0e3404157950ac9bbfdbec3a6","tid":1690348,"uid":243446,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"Black bloc係一定要 唔係嘅話真係唔知邊啲係手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"呢個係畀和理非"},{"pid":"28f07cead3a1b1c4d8869186d54857b6d16e72ef","tid":1690348,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"最緊要係大家要有即出既心"},{"pid":"1df2e35025cbe911af120d1924e567634a31311e","tid":1690348,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n（求人手置頂）【Twitter戰線】加入共識Channel + 有方法避免Twitter當bot同封帳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690328</a><br />\n- 分享